{"tha-ap173:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap173:0.2":"Kumudavagga ","tha-ap173:0.3":"Kumudamaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap173:1.1":"“Pabbate himavantamhi, ","tha-ap173:1.2":"mahajatassaro ahu; ","tha-ap173:1.3":"Tatthajo rakkhaso asim, ","tha-ap173:1.4":"ghorarupo mahabbalo. ","tha-ap173:2.1":"Kumudam pupphate tattha, ","tha-ap173:2.2":"cakkamattani jayare; ","tha-ap173:2.3":"Ocinami ca tam puppham, ","tha-ap173:2.4":"balino samitim tada. ","tha-ap173:3.1":"Atthadassi tu bhagava, ","tha-ap173:3.2":"dvipadindo narasabho; ","tha-ap173:3.3":"Pupphasankocitam disva, ","tha-ap173:3.4":"agacchi mama santikam. ","tha-ap173:4.1":"Upagatanca sambuddham, ","tha-ap173:4.2":"devadevam narasabham; ","tha-ap173:4.3":"Sabbanca puppham paggayha, ","tha-ap173:4.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap173:5.1":"Yavata himavantanta, ","tha-ap173:5.2":"parisa sa tada ahu; ","tha-ap173:5.3":"Tavacchadanasampanno, ","tha-ap173:5.4":"agamasi tathagato. ","tha-ap173:6.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap173:6.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap173:6.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap173:6.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap173:7.1":"Ito pannarase kappe, ","tha-ap173:7.2":"sattahesum janadhipa; ","tha-ap173:7.3":"Sahassarathanama te, ","tha-ap173:7.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap173:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap173:8.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap173:8.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap173:8.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap173:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kumudamaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap173:10.1":"Kumudamaliyattherassapadanam pathamam. "}